title: Post I saw a couple of months ago got me thinking, and I noticed something about my dog this morning.
13 years later and my dog still does this to me when I lay on the floor....
Apparently /r/aww is too good for my perro con sombrero, so I share him with you.
He let out a horrible fart. Then just started at me. Proud of the smell he made.
My dog Maya (rear) is a weird mutt that doesn't really look like any other dog. Then one day at the park, this happened.
Every time she wants attention. Then hugs you when you pet her.
Seriously, guy? You're gonna do that instead of playing with me?
I work at a BMW/MINI dealership. This is how I am greeted by our office dog Cooper every morning.
Heard a door creak, turned around to see this...she stayed staring at me for a good while before testing the limits and pushing the door open further
/r/AWW didn't like her, maybe you guys will. This is what i wake up to every morning.
